Subject: Re: [T2] VW Tent question

It's only important for the "link" (corners and top center) pieces, not 
the poles. Look at this picture: 
http://i6.photobucket.com/albums/y240/duneitrite/3495.jpg

The link pieces are made so the poles running perpendicular to the bus 
can tilt slightly. If you reverse them, the frame won't sit upright - 
it will tilt away from the bus.

